      <title>特斯拉展示 Optimus Gen 2 机器人，其双手得到改进，身材更苗条</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/tesla-optimus-gen-2-new-video-shows-dancing-robot-better-movement-updates</link>
